lead_paragraph: Adrian Peterson was placed on injured reserve Friday by the Minnesota Vikings, another sign that his time with the team could be over following surgery to repair a torn meniscus in his right knee.

headline.print_headline: Vikings Put Peterson on IR; Kalil Has Labral Surgery on Hip
